'''Izable''' was one of the five fortified outposts built by the [[Sons and Daughters of Freedom|Freedom's Sons]] around the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] during the [[Battle of Praesitlyn]], and was the closest of these to the enemy lines, being placed six hundred [[Meter/Legends|meters]] ahead of redoubts [[Eliey]] and [[Kaudine]]. Spotters stationed at this fort were charged with giving advanced warning of any changes in the disposition of the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] forces. During the battle, it was attacked by [[Pors Tonith/Legends|Pors Tonith's]] invading droid army seven times, taken three times, and retaken after the first two attempts. Its armaments, including several [[E-Web heavy repeating blaster/Legends|E-Web heavy repeating blaster]] emplacements, covered a three-hundred-sixty-degree area of fire.

Izable was commanded by [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[D'Nore]]. [[Erk H'Arman]] and [[Odie Subu]] also fought at this redoubt.

